title: Kylie Jenner, Tyga enjoy cell phone date in Calabasas
text:
Seems like there is a third person between Kylie Jenner and Tyga.technology.
READ: â€‹ Tyga hints at engagement to Kylie Jenner, calls her 'fiance'
The 18-year-old reality star and her rapper boyfriend were recently pictured on a dinner date in Calabasas, where both of them were seen looking into their phones rather than talking to each other, reports the Mirror. In one snap, Jenner could be seen texting on her phone, while Tyga is just staring into the distance with his hand in her hands. The pair started dating in 2014.
